@startuml
!include ../includes/appsec-style.puml
title AppSec Process 05: Secret Scanning Response (GHAS)

' Purpose: Rapidly contain credential exposure with clear ownership (AppCode) and repeatable rotation.

start

partition "Detect" {
  :GHAS secret scanning alert;
  :Identify AppCode (repo/app mapping);
}

partition "Contain" {
  :Revoke/rotate secret;
  :Invalidate sessions/tokens as needed;
  :Remove secret from code + history;
}

partition "Assess" {
  if (Exposed in public or broad scope?) then (Yes)
    :Escalate incident response;
  else (No)
    :Standard response;
  endif
}

partition "Prevent" {
  :Add secret to allow/deny patterns;
  :Add pre-commit hooks / scanning checks;
  :Update developer guidance;
}

partition "Close" {
  :Confirm rotation + no reuse;
  :Close alert + track metrics (AppCode);
}

note right
Key message: **Contain first, then learn**.
AppCode ensures notifications reach the right owners.
end note

stop
@enduml
